{
  "stem": "142.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But before, every six months they would change the sonderkommando with new ones, because always there were people coming in for the same purpose, you know.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But you know, always you go-- I used to go by, if I am alive the next day.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That-- that was always my-- my vision, was not to go in front of the Germans, always, because I made up my mind that that war will be ending one day.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I want to be-- if I'm alive, I want to be the guy to tell the story.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, very soon, you know, because I knew that, you know, I didn't have too much time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I have to find ways to see.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, I was always observing what was happening.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Every day, you know, our-- the Germans were really some-- most of them were very tough people, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't want us around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't have too much to do with them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were only 30 days of-- and then after the 30 days, we were already in the sonderkommando.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was-- that was a selection.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They selected, I think at that time, if I remember, they selected 35 Greeks to go into the sonderkommando.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's all I know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, yeah, they came one day, and they-- we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They selected a new one to block 13.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew that block 13 was the sonderkommando.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Physically?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was part of the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, you know, I don't know exactly the route or where exactly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it wasn't too far away, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It just.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't-- they didn't let us know too much about.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew that we had to work day and night, our 12-hour shift.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
